    "body": "So, probably need find why block execution does write 275 receipts(instead of 276): `eth/stagedsync/stage_execute.go -> SpawnExecuteBlocksStage -> executeBlock -> AppendReceipts`\r\n\r\nCan re-exec blocks next way:\r\n```\r\n#first unwind to block < 14794507\r\ngo run --trimpath  ./cmd/integration state_stages --unwind=1 --datadir=<your_datadir> --chain=bsc --integrity.fast=false\r\n\r\n#then run forward to block 14794507\r\ngo run --trimpath  ./cmd/integration state_stages --block=14794507  --datadir=<your_datadir> --chain=bsc --integrity.fast=false\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
